      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink33">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi makiḻnaṉ</l>
          <l> marutuyarn tōṅkiya viripūm peruntuṟaip</l>
          <l> peṇṭirō ṭāṭu meṉpataṉ</l>
          <l> ṟaṇṭā rakalan talaittalaik koḷavē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> Alas, [my] friend!</l>
          <l> The man who brings delight </l>
          <l>–so they say–</l>
          <l> bathes with [his] women</l>
          <l> in the big ghat with flowers that blossom up high in the tops of the myrobalan trees,</l>
          <l> so that one head after another rests on his cool garlanded chest.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
